text: Benoit Marie (born December 26, 1992) is a Seychellois football player. He is a Defender playing for the Seychelles national football team and has represented Seychelles in the AFCON 2018. == References == Category:Living people Category:1992 births Category:Seychellois footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:Seychelles international footballers
